#: ../../doc/index.rst:2
msgid "asbind20: C++20 AngelScript binding library"
msgstr "asbind20：C++20 AngelScript 绑定库"

#: ../../doc/index.rst:4
msgid ""
"**asbind20** is a C++20 `AngelScript <https://www.angelcode.com/angelscript/"
">`_ binding library powered by templates."
msgstr ""
"**asbind20** 是一个由模板驱动的 C++20 `AngelScript <https://"
"www.angelcode.com/angelscript/>`_ 绑定库。"

#: ../../doc/index.rst:6
msgid ""
"Although the interface of AngelScript is very friendly to C++ compared to "
"most binding APIs from other script languages, it still needs many "
"additional proxy functions, e.g., when binding a constructor. However, most "
"of these proxies have similar logic, so they can be generated by some "
"template tricks."
msgstr ""
"尽管与大多数其他脚本语言的绑定 API 相比，AngelScript 的接口对 C++ 非常友好，"
"但它仍然需要许多额外的代理函数，例如在绑定构造函数时。然而，大多数这些代理函"
"数具有相似的逻辑，因此可以通过一些模板技巧来生成。"

#: ../../doc/index.rst:10
msgid ""
"Besides, this library provides tools for easily calling a script function, "
"as well as RAII helpers for managing lifetime of AngelScript objects."
msgstr ""
"此外，本库提供了轻松调用脚本函数的工具，以及用于管理 AngelScript 对象生命周期"
"的 RAII 辅助工具。"

#: ../../doc/index.rst:13
msgid ""
"In general, this library aims to automate everything that can be generated "
"by template meta-programming."
msgstr "总的来说，本库旨在自动化所有可以通过模板元编程生成的内容。"

#: ../../doc/index.rst:15
msgid ""
"The name and API design are inspired by the famous `pybind11 library "
"<https://github.com/pybind/pybind11>`_."
msgstr ""
"名称和 API 设计的灵感来自著名的 `pybind11 库 <https://github.com/pybind/"
"pybind11>`_。"

#: ../../doc/index.rst:18
msgid "Core Features"
msgstr "核心特性"

#: ../../doc/index.rst:20
msgid ""
"Conveniently bind C++ functions / classes to AngelScript, including auto-"
"generated wrappers for constructors / factories / operators."
msgstr ""
"方便地将 C++ 函数/类绑定到 AngelScript，包括自动生成的构造函数/工厂/运算符包"
"装器。"

#: ../../doc/index.rst:23
msgid ""
"Tools for passing arguments to and receiving return value from script "
"functions, without manually choosing the correct function for different "
"types."
msgstr ""
"用于向脚本函数传递参数和接收返回值的工具，无需手动为不同类型选择正确的函数。"

#: ../../doc/index.rst:26
msgid ""
"Generating a generic wrapper for functions of any parameter count at compile-"
"time, without using any macro."
msgstr "在编译时为任意参数数量的函数生成泛型包装器，无需使用任何宏。"

#: ../../doc/index.rst:29
msgid "RAII tools for managing lifetime of script objects."
msgstr "用于管理脚本对象生命周期的 RAII 工具。"

#: ../../doc/index.rst:31
msgid "Container for storing script objects."
msgstr "用于存储脚本对象的容器。"

